dotfiles
========

Important
---------
Download tmux terminfo database:
	$ curl -LO http://invisible-island.net/datafiles/current/terminfo.src.gz
	$ gunzip terminfo.src.gz
	$ tic -x terminfo.src

To set up hardware acceleration in Firefox see commit b689980

Usage
-----
cd ~
git clone --recurse-submodules <url>
cd dotfiles
stow *
mkdir ~/.local/share/x11  # for Xauthority

GNU Stow â€“ https://www.gnu.org/software/stow/
